{
  "stem": "10818.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My-- my grandmother had a lot of relatives there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my grandfather got into business, first with his brother-in-law, my mother's-- my grandmother's brother, and then with somebody else who had an established wine business.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- so my father and my grandfathers were partners.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they stayed in this-- this was, you know, in the '20s, early '20s.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they stayed in this business until 1938 when they were forced by the government to give up the business.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they sold it to one of their employees who had connections in the party.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the-- whatever the proceeds of the sale were, were very low.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father was in touch with the man who bought it after the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But he didn't want it back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, obviously he was here, and he did-- he-- he was-- he was not-- no longer interested in retrieving it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he was interested in how it was going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I don't know what happened to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it-- it was-- was--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the late '30s.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, in the late '30s.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, it was a combination of the Nuremberg laws, and-- and then later on, there were laws when-- when Jews weren't allowed to be in business at all anymore.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, the German population was not allowed to-- to-- to buy from Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, this-- you know, it was a two-way street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, my father and my grandfather had seen this coming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they started visiting Holland, the Netherlands, and had a good clientele there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they were able to carry this business on for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they were sort of in touch with all kinds of things before Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
